      "message": "There was a bug where editing the Task Logic field could silently drop changes. It was caused by the `editAreaLoader.init` call below not finding the function \"onEditAreaChanged\". Edit Area uses an iframe and looks for the callback using \"window.parent.onEditAreaChanged\". Injecting it to the document makes it accessible.",
